\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Light Wind: }{\fs20\cf0 A gentle breeze, having little or no game effect.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Moderate Wind: }{\fs20\cf0 A steady wind with a 50% chance of extinguishing small, unprotected flames, such as candles.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Strong Wind: }{\fs20\cf0 Gusts that automatically extinguish unprotected flames (candles, torches, and the like). Such gusts impose a \endash 2 penalty on ranged attack rolls and on Listen checks.
\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Severe Wind: }{\fs20\cf0 In addition to 
