\par }{\fs20\cf0 Darkvision allows many characters and monsters to see perfectly well without any light at all, but characters with normal vision (or low-light vi
sion, for that matter) can be rendered completely blind by putting out the lights. Torches or lanterns can be blown out by sudden gusts of subterranean wind, magical light sources can be dispelled or countered, or magical traps might create fields of impe
